******
[2] Santiago Metropolitan District
Date: Sun 18 Mar 2018
Source: Publimetro [in Spanish, trans. Mod.TY, edited
https://www.publimetro.cl/cl/noticias/2018/03/18/maxima-preocupacion-pirque-luego-del-contagio-trabajador-virus-hanta.html


There is considerable worry in the Pirque community generated by a confirmed case of [a] hantavirus [infection]. According to a municipal communication, the man was working on the El Cardo farm in San Juan. The announcement indicated that, although the exact location where he was infected is unknown, it is requested that maximum precautions be taken in the area between the Cerro de San Juan to Santa Rita.

"For now, we must take all the necessary precautions, such as clearing areas where one is going to camp and airing out sheds and houses in areas near these places," the announcement stated.

[byline: Camilo Henr√≠quez]

